&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum requirements for the role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years in Product Marketing with a focus on B2B SaaS or Management Consulting experience with a focus on enterprise sales and go to market.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrate a mission-critical, commercial mindset with deep empathy for B2B sales channels and experience helping them win deals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a proactive, resilient self-starter who thrives in ambiguity and takes full ownership to drive complex problems to a solution.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have executive presence and polished communication skills, with the credibility to &quot;command a room&quot; and present to senior leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
